            "object": "text",
            "leaves": [
              {
                "text": "The most important problems in science are increasingly interdisciplinary [x]"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "object": "block",
        "type": "paragraph",
        "nodes": [
          {
            "object": "text",
            "leaves": [
              {
                "text": "This means we have a growing interdisciplinary \"burden of knowledge\" [x] - intuitively, the “overhead” we have to pay to get into a position to do the science is getting bigger and bigger"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "object": "block",
        "type": "paragraph",
        "nodes": [
          {
            "object": "text",
            "leaves": [
              {
                "text": "We’re coping with this (for now)..."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },

      {
        "object": "block",
        "type": "bulleted-list",
        "nodes": [
          {
            "object": "block",
            "type": "list-item",
            "nodes": [
              {
                "object": "text",
                "leaves": [
                  {
                    "text": "With more specialized education [x]"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "object": "block",
        "type": "bulleted-list",
        "nodes": [
          {
            "object": "block",
            "type": "list-item",
            "nodes": [
              {
                "object": "text",
                "leaves": [
                  {
                    "text": "Scientists are increasingly older when they win a Nobel prize and when they get their first PhD [x]"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "object": "block",
        "type": "bulleted-list",
        "nodes": [
          {
            "object": "block",
            "type": "list-item",
            "nodes": [
              {
                "object": "text",
                "leaves": [
                  {
                    "text": "By doing more science in teams [x]"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "object": "block",
        "type": "paragraph",
        "nodes": [
          {
            "object": "text",
            "leaves": [
              {
                "text": "But how long can this last? We’re starting to see some signs of strain"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "object": "block",
        "type": "bulleted-list",
        "nodes": [
          {
            "object": "block",
            "type": "list-item",
            "nodes": [
              {
                "object": "text",
                "leaves": [
                  {
                    "text": "While research effort has skyrocketed, research productivity (ratio of impact/breakthroughs to effort) has stagnated or declined [x]"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "object": "block",
        "type": "paragraph",
        "nodes": [
          {
            "object": "text",
            "leaves": [
              {
                "text": "Primary conjecture: the growing interdisciplinary burden of knowledge is straining the infrastructure we use to synthesize knowledge"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "object": "block",
        "type": "paragraph",
        "nodes": [
          {
            "object": "text",
            "leaves": [
              {
                "text": "Infrastructure is invisible until it fails"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "object": "block",
        "type": "paragraph",
        "nodes": [
          {
            "object": "text",
            "leaves": [
              {
                "text": "Primary “big question”: What infrastructures can we build to secure the long-term health of open, collaborative, interdisciplinary science?"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
